com.vmware.nsx_policy.global_infra

Class GlobalInfraFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.global_infra.GlobalInfraFactory

  • public class GlobalInfraFactory
extends Object
    GlobalInfraFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.global_infra package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
